bug.short_desc: qx.ui.container.Drawer is broken on Windows Phone 8

long_desc.thetext: If you have a look at the Drawer example in the mobile showcase, you will notice that the contents of the drawer are not visible. Instead, the drawer seems to be transparent and you see all the underlying stuff.
Created attachment 1360 Pic of the transparent drawer on a WP8 device
